Package: GroupMeanSummarization
Title: Summarize the Data using Group Mean
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Shreya", "Verma", , "shreyav1@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The package automates the calculation of arithmetic mean.
    Additionally, the user can choose to group the data at any single or multiple levels.
    For convenience, user can select data grouping via column index(es) or name(s).
